  dialogue:
  - I see...
  - If you want to come with, you need to fetch some stuff for me.
  - Got it.
  - Get my fishing rod and harpoon.
  - The rod's by the house...
  - ...and the harpoon's by the lighthouse.
  - Why a harpoon?
  - Won't feel safe without it.
  - Set them up somewhere on the boat when you bring them here.
  - Now get!
